{
  "title": "AD #5 · Sleep for Health (Path B)",
  "lessons": [
    {
      "translation": "Claire 说饮食最重要，Paul 说定期体检最重要。两者都有用，但我认为最重要的习惯是每晚睡好。",
      "phrases": ["Claire says", "a good diet matters most,", "Paul says", "regular checkups matter most.", "Both are useful,", "but I believe", "the one habit that matters most", "is sleeping well every night."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "睡眠不只是众多健康习惯之一，它是让其他习惯真正生效的底层。",
      "phrases": ["Sleep is not just", "one healthy habit", "among many.", "It is the base layer", "that lets the other habits", "actually do their job."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "先想想 Claire 的观点。均衡饮食给身体原料，但睡眠不足时饥饿激素失衡，身体也无法好好处理食物。",
      "phrases": ["Think about Claire's point first.", "A balanced diet", "gives the body", "its raw materials.", "But when we do not sleep enough,", "the hunger hormones", "go out of balance", "and the body", "does not process food well."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "睡眠差的情况下，健康食物也帮不上太多忙。",
      "phrases": ["Even healthy food", "cannot help much", "on top of bad sleep."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "Paul 的观点也有同样的问题。体检能早发现，但很多现代疾病——高血压、二型糖尿病、记忆力衰退——都生长于多年的睡眠不足。",
      "phrases": ["Paul's idea has", "the same problem.", "A checkup can find something early,", "but many modern diseases —", "high blood pressure,", "type-2 diabetes,", "memory loss —", "grow out of", "years of poor sleep."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "年度体检能抓到它们，但无法逆转它们。",
      "phrases": ["A yearly visit", "can catch them", "but cannot undo them."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "相比之下，睡眠让身体持续运转。",
      "phrases": ["Sleep, by contrast,", "keeps the body running."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "深度睡眠时，大脑清除废物，免疫系统重建，肌肉修复。",
      "phrases": ["During deep sleep,", "the brain clears out waste,", "the immune system rebuilds,", "and muscles repair."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "英国 Whitehall 研究发现，每晚睡眠不足六小时的成年人心脏病风险高出近 50%。",
      "phrases": ["The Whitehall study in the UK", "found that adults", "who sleep less than six hours a night", "have nearly 50% higher", "heart-disease risk."]
    },
    {
      "translation": "饮食和体检是有用的修补手段；睡眠是让一切运转的静默工作。",
      "phrases": ["Diet and checkups", "are useful fixes;", "sleep is the quiet work", "that keeps everything else working."]
    }
  ]
